column5: Hey everyone, has anybody been to port Albert lately? Going muskie fishing this week, but when i return I'm in the hunt for the silver bullet!
i made a report like yours the other day and all i got was nothing like the fishing is there right now! NOTHING.....any day now though they are gonna start moving around....
Where did you get your nickname?

well i'm back from my weekend of musky fishing and got skunked. Well shouldn't say that, I caught a bass and walleye. Both were a release for I was out there for the monster. I guess it's time for the silver bullet now, and just wondering are they in port albert yet? Or the 21 bridge?
check Grey-Bruce outdoors forum for that info.
deadsville..........another couple of weeks or a couple of inches of rain.
